          francais:
              " Mā Qaţa`tum Min Līnatin 'Aw Taraktumūhā Qā'imatan `Alá 'Uşūlihā Fabi'idhni Allāhi Wa Liyukhziya Al-Fāsiqīna",
          wolof:
